.TH LOOTSHEET-CODEX-SEARCH 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-codex-search \\- Search codex entries by name, title, location, faction, class, race, or notes
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet codex search [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Subcommand: codex search

Search codex entries by name, title, location, faction, class, race, description, or notes content.

Flags:
  --query   search query (required)

Examples:
  lootsheet codex search --query "thieves guild"
  lootsheet codex search --query "Fighter"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for search
.TP
--query=string
search query (required) (default: )
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-codex(1)
